import { Paper, Typography, Stack, Box } from "@material-ui/core";


function MetaData() {
    return (
        <Paper component={Stack} spacing={2} sx={{ width: 2 / 4, alignSelf: 'center', mt: '1rem', p: 2 }}>
            <Box>
                <Typography fontSize='1.4rem' fontWeight='500' color='#1A237E'>About</Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Typography fontSize='1.4rem' fontWeight='500' color='#1A237E'>Credits</Typography>
                <Typography>Icons</Typography>
                <Typography>
                FlatIcons: Icons by 
                <Box component='a' href="https://www.freepik.com" display='inline'> Freepik </Box>
                From 
                <Box component='a'href="https://www.flaticon.com/" display='inline'> FlatIcons.</Box>
                </Typography>
                <Typography>
                Material UI Icons: Icons by 
                <Box component='a' href="https://www.freepik.com" display='inline'> Freepik </Box>
                From 
                <Box component='a'href="https://www.flaticon.com/" display='inline'> FlatIcons.</Box>
                </Typography>
            </Box>
        </Paper>
    )
}

export default MetaData;
